com.complexible.common.hash

Class ConcatenatedPrimitiveSink<T extends PrimitiveSink>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.complexible.common.hash.ConcatenatedPrimitiveSink<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PrimitiveSink, Iterable<T>

    public final class ConcatenatedPrimitiveSink<T extends PrimitiveSink>
extends Object
implements PrimitiveSink, Iterable<T>

    An implementation of PrimitiveSink which has a number of 'child' sinks to which each call to this Sink is delegated. Intended to make it easy to multiplex results to a list of sinks.

    Since:
    2.3
